Biggest Little Investments LP


                  Biggest Little Investments LP provides real estate services to residential and commercial customers. It operates acquisition and ownership of real estate properties for investment in senior and junior accrued interest mortgage loans. The company was founded in 1986 and is headquartered in Reno, NV.                




Co-Chairman, Chief Financial Officer, Secretary & Treasurer

