Ben  Farahi
BEN FARAHI has been Co-Chairman of the Board, Chief Financial
Officer, Secretary, and Treasurer of Monarch since its inception,
and of Golden Road since June 1993. From 1973 until June 1993,
Mr. Farahi was Secretary, Treasurer, and a Director of Golden
